cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.RO, cs.SY, cs.CV

The paper proposes a model-based reinforcement learning algorithm with attention mechanism embedded for control problems. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.RO (Robotics). The paper also mentions the use of variational auto-encoder (VAE) and recurrent neural network (RNN), which are commonly used in computer vision (cs.CV) and system engineering (cs.SY) fields, respectively. Therefore, these two sub-categories are also likely.
